The Proton · node ATM · ATM · A nucleon built of three quarks (up-up-down), one of the two residents of the nucleus. Positively charged, effectively stable (lifetime > 10³⁴ years).

universe of origin : ATM · The Atom
seal               : ITS COUNT IS THE ELEMENT. The number of protons (the atomic number, Z) is the atom's identity — 1 proton is hydrogen, 6 is carbon, 79 is gold. Change the proton count and you change the element itself.
